libsoup: libsoup (HTTP library)
libsoup:
libsoup: libsoup is an HTTP client/server library for GNOME. It uses GObjects 
libsoup: and the glib main loop, to integrate well with GNOME applications. It 
libsoup: features both asynchronous and synchronous APIs, SSL Support using
libsoup: GnuTLS, proxy support, including authentication and SSL tunneling,
libsoup: client support for Digest, NTLM, and Basic authentication, server
libsoup: support for Digest and Basic authentication, and basic client-side 
libsoup: SOAP and XML-RPC support.
libsoup:
